    <h2 class="h2" style="margin-bottom:10px;">Cleanup is scoped in three tiers.</h2>
    <p class="lede" style="margin:0 0 24px;max-width:72ch;">QuickBooks cleanup is sized to what the file actually needs. These are the canonical tier figures from the service pages &mdash; the free file review tells you honestly which tier fits. Catch-up bookkeeping is priced separately by how many periods are behind.</p>
    <table class="cmp">
